mac node + mongo + redis:

1. install xcode.
2. install homebrew: google homebrew and open terminal, paste the code below:
	ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"

3. use homebrew to install nodejs:
	brew install nodejs
	node --version

4. use homebrew to install mongodb:
	brew install mongodb
   check the mongo version:
    mongo --version

5. use homebrew to install redis and check version:
	brew install redis
	redis-cli --version
